        </c02>
      </c01>
      <c01 level="series">
        <did>
          <unittitle>Sermons</unittitle>
        </did>
        <scopecontent>
          <p>The Sermons series has been arranged by date (when known). If undated, individual sermons have been arranged by title or scripture verse on which the sermon was based. Most of these sermons are handwritten. A small portion of them have been published.</p>
        </scopecontent>
